//! Wire format substrate for `std::encoding::wire`.
//!
//! This module held the legacy HBF byte-layout helpers (`encode_header`,
//! `decode_header`, `validate_header`). Those helpers were removed when
//! the CBOR envelope substrate (`hew-runtime/src/envelope.rs`) became the sole
//! internode encoding. The opaque `Value` contract for user-facing stdlib
//! encoding modules lives in `value_trait.hew` and remains active.
